  "texts": [
    "Experimental results and analysisWe gathered 2746 documents from MEC devices like traffic lights, cameras, mobile phones, and vehicles, covering situations such as traffic and travel.",
    "Additionally, we included 582 authoritative meteorological forecast documents from the Jiangsu Provincial Meteorological Bureau into our dataset.",
    "To encompass daily situations like dialogue and news, we collected 1056 documents using a theme crawler program from sources like Wikipedia, Baidu Baike, and major news websites.",
    "After a rigorous screening process, we utilized 4097 documents to construct the final dataset, with an average word count of 1052 per document.",
    "Based on this amalgamated dataset, we employ NLP methods such as word segmentation, part of speech tagging, and NER to finish in feature extraction and data integration, ultimately constructing a knowledge graph."
